      Press release
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Government confirms plans to introduce import controls
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Today, the government has confirmed plans to introduce import controls on EU goods at the border after the transition period ends on 31 December 2020.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
